        let's redefine how APIs collaborate. Be part of the future; let's craft together.
      </p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-x-4 mt-8">
        <a
          target="_blank"
          href="https://spec.open-federation.org/"
          class="bg-black hover:opacity-80 px-6 py-3 text-white transition-colors">Open Spec</a
        >
        <button id="typeform" class="text-black px-6 py-3 border hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">Subscribe</button>
